         ♪ Sweat break

17:04.223 --> 17:06.759
             ♪ Hot

17:09.695 --> 17:12.297
               So, what are we
                gonna steal?

17:12.366 --> 17:14.833
  Everything, baby.

17:14.901 --> 17:16.701
Absolutely everything.

17:16.703 --> 17:19.637
                     ♪♪

17:25.079 --> 17:26.944
                How you gonna
           fence all this stuff?

17:27.012 --> 17:30.449
I have a friend back East.
She'll hold an estate sale.

17:31.685 --> 17:33.618
      How much
   will you clear?

17:33.687 --> 17:35.620
               60 to 100 grand
             for the furniture.

17:35.622 --> 17:38.290
               Another $30,000
         for the rugs and china.

17:38.358 --> 17:42.227
Expensive wine she'll put
on eBay, one bottle at a time.

17:42.229 --> 17:44.763
The rest goes to a caterer
     in Arizona.

17:46.633 --> 17:48.233
           You trust these guys?

17:48.235 --> 17:50.235
      She does.

17:50.237 --> 17:51.836
 They work for her.

17:51.906 --> 17:54.773
                    Guns?
        Nope.

17:54.841 --> 17:56.575
                None of 'em?

17:56.643 --> 17:58.176
      No one's
shooting anyone over

17:58.245 --> 18:00.279
   some furniture
  and copper pots.

18:01.381 --> 18:03.115
           Well, in that case...

18:03.183 --> 18:04.383
                   cheers.

18:07.521 --> 18:10.122
When are we gonna get the rest
of our money, Smurf?

18:10.190 --> 18:12.391
                "Hello, Mom.
                How are you?"

18:12.459 --> 18:14.793
               I'm good, baby.
                How are you?

18:14.861 --> 18:16.228
                   "Fine."

18:19.199 --> 18:20.732
    I need my cut
 of the Lucy money.

18:20.801 --> 18:23.201
                 Sounds like
          you're in a big hurry.

18:23.270 --> 18:25.337
I'm buying something.

18:25.405 --> 18:27.872
                Really? What?

18:27.874 --> 18:29.341
      A house.

18:29.409 --> 18:30.675
                   Where?

18:30.677 --> 18:33.245
     On Pacific,
   near Chair Six.

18:34.014 --> 18:36.081
                Good for you.

18:36.150 --> 18:40.052
        Too old to sleep in that
     crawl space above your bar.

18:41.221 --> 18:44.156
Yeah, we looked at the place
this morning, made an offer.

18:46.693 --> 18:48.560
                 Who's "we"?

18:48.629 --> 18:51.463
       Adrian.
He's moving in with me.

18:53.834 --> 18:56.235
              Adrian putting up
                 any money?

18:57.838 --> 19:00.372
   Am I gonna get
my cut or not, Smurf?

19:00.441 --> 19:03.308
           How much do you need?

19:03.377 --> 19:05.109
    $1.3 million.

19:05.111 --> 19:06.445
          [ Whisking ]

19:06.513 --> 19:09.314
   You know, prices are going up
             down by the beach.

19:09.316 --> 19:10.949
         You getting a mortgage?

19:12.386 --> 19:13.918
  Yes or no, Smurf?

19:13.988 --> 19:15.788
     [ Whisking continues ]

19:15.856 --> 19:18.190
                 No problem.
       Will you stay for dinner?

19:18.258 --> 19:20.459
    No, I can't.

19:20.527 --> 19:21.994
            What about tomorrow?

19:22.062 --> 19:23.528
        I'll make fried chicken.

19:23.597 --> 19:25.664
           You can bring Adrian.

19:25.732 --> 19:28.667
      [ Cellphone ringing ]

19:33.808 --> 19:35.407
             Hello?

19:39.213 --> 19:45.484
                     ♪♪

19:45.552 --> 19:47.619
               Morgan's dead.

19:47.688 --> 19:50.955
                     ♪♪

19:50.957 --> 19:52.224
         [ Tool clangs ]

19:52.292 --> 19:57.696
                     ♪♪

19:57.764 --> 20:00.833
   [ Indistinct conversation ]

20:00.901 --> 20:05.570
                     ♪♪

20:05.572 --> 20:07.372
      Everything all right?

20:07.374 --> 20:10.376
 Oh, fine. Hi, baby.
     Going out?

20:12.246 --> 20:13.912
  Have a nice day.

20:13.980 --> 20:22.320
                     ♪♪

20:22.389 --> 20:30.995
                     ♪♪

20:30.997 --> 20:32.464
         [ Keys jingle ]

20:32.533 --> 20:34.799
        [ Engine starts ]

20:34.869 --> 20:37.002
                     ♪♪

20:38.805 --> 20:41.540
  He should, um...
 be back any minute.

20:41.608 --> 20:46.144
[ El Dusty's "We Out Chea" plays
         in background ]

20:46.213 --> 20:48.280
         [ Keys jingle ]

20:48.348 --> 20:55.420
                     ♪♪

20:55.489 --> 20:57.422
      [ Engine shuts off ]

20:57.424 --> 20:59.091
    There he is.

20:59.159 --> 21:05.097
                     ♪♪

21:05.165 --> 21:08.100
   [ Indistinct conversation ]

21:08.168 --> 21:11.503
                     ♪♪

21:11.572 --> 21:14.306
I need you to finish it.

21:14.375 --> 21:15.908
                    When?

21:15.976 --> 21:21.780
                     ♪♪

21:21.848 --> 21:27.519
                     ♪♪

21:27.588 --> 21:29.053
     Pete: Mia!

21:29.055 --> 21:30.556
                 <i> ¿Qué pasa?</i>

21:33.928 --> 21:35.594
       We need
  to take a drive.

21:35.662 --> 21:37.129
                I'm not done
            with the orders yet.

21:37.197 --> 21:39.131
    Yes, you are.
      Let's go.

21:39.199 --> 21:46.071
                     ♪♪

21:46.140 --> 21:55.680
                     ♪♪

21:55.749 --> 21:57.682
                    Wait.
               Wait a second.

21:57.684 --> 21:59.017
               Don't you think
              we should leave?

21:59.085 --> 22:01.686
           Every time
       I finish a big job,

22:01.688 --> 22:04.123
         I like to reward myself
            with a little treat.

22:06.026 --> 22:07.492
     Ice cream?

22:07.561 --> 22:09.161
             You ever freebase?

22:09.229 --> 22:11.563
            I brought some rocks
                to celebrate.

22:11.632 --> 22:20.639
                     ♪♪

22:20.707 --> 22:22.507
             Where are we going?

22:22.576 --> 22:28.981
                     ♪♪

22:29.049 --> 22:32.116
                Can I turn on
                 some music?
Pete: Leave it off.

22:32.118 --> 22:36.588
                     ♪♪

22:36.657 --> 22:39.124
I told you we were done
with the Codys, huh?

22:40.126 --> 22:42.461
Told you to stay away
 from them,<i> que no?</i>

22:43.864 --> 22:46.465
How long you been spreading
your legs for that <i> Nieto?</i>

22:47.734 --> 22:49.535
         Couple months.

22:52.072 --> 22:53.605
           I like him.

22:53.674 --> 22:55.874
        He lets me sleep
          at his house.

22:55.942 --> 22:57.810
             Giving it up cheap,
                   <i> chica.</i>

22:57.878 --> 22:59.277
      What about you,<i> puta?</i>

22:59.346 --> 23:01.146
     You still giving it up
     for that <i> tonto,</i> Spider?

23:01.215 --> 23:03.081
 Hey, hey, hey, hey!
      <i> iBasta!</i>

23:03.150 --> 23:05.451
   <i> iBasta, puta!</i>
  You knock it off!

23:07.154 --> 23:09.488
 You better get this
through your head, huh.

23:09.556 --> 23:12.057
    This ain't no
Romeo and Juliet shit.

23:14.695 --> 23:17.496
      And you.
You ain't no Juliet,<i> puta.</i>

23:17.564 --> 23:20.632
[ Insecure Men's "Subaru Nights"
             plays ]

23:20.701 --> 23:28.973
                     ♪♪

23:28.975 --> 23:36.915
                     ♪♪

23:36.983 --> 23:44.256
                     ♪♪

23:44.324 --> 23:49.261
    ♪ My pock-faced darling

23:49.329 --> 23:53.065
     ♪ Pebble-dash morning

23:53.133 --> 23:58.336
        ♪ Yours forever

23:58.405 --> 24:04.076
            ♪ Mine

24:04.144 --> 24:09.147
  ♪ My heart beat's stalling

24:09.216 --> 24:13.285
   ♪ Pleather starts falling

24:13.353 --> 24:18.290
        ♪ Yours forever

24:18.358 --> 24:24.897
            ♪ Mine

24:24.965 --> 24:31.370
                     ♪♪

24:31.438 --> 24:37.709
                     ♪♪

24:37.778 --> 24:39.644
      [ Engine shuts off ]

24:39.713 --> 24:43.248
                     ♪♪

24:45.119 --> 24:46.285
                  Smurf: J.

24:50.390 --> 24:52.324
               Morgan is dead.

24:52.392 --> 24:53.859
                She drowned.

24:55.996 --> 24:57.529
        How?

24:57.598 --> 25:00.599
              Boating accident,
                 they think.

25:02.669 --> 25:05.069
  [ Sighs ] Jesus.

25:05.071 --> 25:09.408
       And she didn't only steal
          one of our properties.

25:09.476 --> 25:11.310
              She stole three.

25:16.216 --> 25:18.683
                 She lifted
               a notary stamp

25:18.685 --> 25:21.153
              from some old guy
               with dementia.

25:24.291 --> 25:27.159
               She used layers
            of holding companies

25:27.227 --> 25:29.094
             to hide the sales.

25:30.965 --> 25:33.498
      Morgan was always smart --

25:33.567 --> 25:34.767
                 very smart.

25:34.835 --> 25:40.773
                     ♪♪

25:40.841 --> 25:43.708
              You're smart, J.

25:43.710 --> 25:46.311
             Are you <i> that</i> smart?

25:46.313 --> 25:54.453
                     ♪♪

25:54.521 --> 25:56.288
          You better be careful.

25:57.524 --> 25:59.324
        Why?

25:59.326 --> 26:00.659
               Well, with Mia.

26:00.727 --> 26:02.194
                I don't want
            another little mouth

26:02.262 --> 26:04.729
             running around here
                  to feed.

26:04.731 --> 26:14.673
                     ♪♪

26:18.078 --> 26:27.018
                     ♪♪

26:27.020 --> 26:28.420
            Frankie?

26:28.489 --> 26:31.490
           [ Grunts ]

26:31.558 --> 26:33.424
            [ Sighs ]

26:33.426 --> 26:39.765
                     ♪♪

26:39.833 --> 26:41.500
            Frankie.

26:41.568 --> 26:47.506
                     ♪♪

26:47.574 --> 26:53.512
                     ♪♪

26:53.580 --> 26:59.318
                     ♪♪

26:59.386 --> 27:03.188
 [ The Blue Stones' "Be My Fire"
      plays in background ]

27:03.256 --> 27:10.729
                     ♪♪

27:10.798 --> 27:13.665
             Deran Cody around?

27:13.667 --> 27:15.134
  Yeah, that's me.

27:15.202 --> 27:17.903
          Tony Casas, California
      Department of Corrections.

27:20.007 --> 27:22.073
        Okay.

27:22.143 --> 27:24.343
                 I'm looking
             for Benito Oxcama.

27:24.411 --> 27:26.045
                  Have you
              seen him around?

27:27.881 --> 27:30.482
           Yeah, not in a while.

27:30.551 --> 27:32.484
       Casas:
  What's "a while"?

27:32.553 --> 27:34.186
                I don't know,
              a couple months.

27:36.357 --> 27:39.358
             Is everything okay?
              Is Ox in trouble?

27:39.426 --> 27:41.360
  He broke parole.

27:41.428 --> 27:44.896
          Okay, well, so, w-what
   does that have to do with me?

27:44.965 --> 27:47.632
               We got you down
           as a known associate.

27:47.701 --> 27:49.701
     [ Scoffs ]

27:49.703 --> 27:52.838
    Man, that was
  a long time ago.

27:52.906 --> 27:54.907
I'm a business owner now.
   This is my bar.

27:56.910 --> 27:58.711
   On the straight
  and narrow, huh?

28:00.247 --> 28:03.482
     Listen, uh,
you see him around...

28:04.518 --> 28:06.117
 ...give me a call.

28:06.187 --> 28:11.322
                     ♪♪

28:11.392 --> 28:16.461
                     ♪♪

28:16.530 --> 28:17.596
      [ Cellphone chimes ]

28:17.664 --> 28:22.534
                     ♪♪

28:22.603 --> 28:24.335
       [ Cellphone locks ]

28:24.337 --> 28:25.737
                     ♪♪

28:25.739 --> 28:28.139
        <i> iCarlos, vamos!</i>

28:28.209 --> 28:31.877
                     ♪♪

28:31.945 --> 28:34.713
      [ Speaking Spanish ]

28:36.617 --> 28:37.883
          <i> Buenos días.</i>

28:37.951 --> 28:40.285
                    <i> Hola.</i>
             [ Sighs ]

28:42.489 --> 28:46.558
                     ♪♪

28:46.627 --> 28:47.626
           [ Gunshot ]

28:47.694 --> 28:52.564
                     ♪♪

28:52.633 --> 28:54.433
         Shh, shh, shh,
            shh, shh.

28:54.501 --> 28:55.767
           <i> Siéntate.</i>

28:55.769 --> 28:58.503
    <i> Quedate y no te muevas.</i>

28:58.572 --> 29:00.305
          <i> ¿Entiendes?</i>

29:02.309 --> 29:03.508
        <i> Sí.</i>

29:03.577 --> 29:12.117
                     ♪♪

29:12.185 --> 29:20.391
                     ♪♪

29:20.461 --> 29:27.398
                     ♪♪

29:27.400 --> 29:34.139
                     ♪♪

29:34.207 --> 29:41.146
                     ♪♪

29:41.214 --> 29:47.686
                     ♪♪

29:47.755 --> 29:54.626
                     ♪♪

29:54.695 --> 30:01.500
                     ♪♪

30:01.568 --> 30:04.069
      [ Telephone ringing ]

30:10.577 --> 30:12.978
       [ Telephone beeps ]
              Yeah?

30:13.046 --> 30:15.347
        Woman: <i> I have a delivery</i>
              <i> for Janine Cody.</i>

30:17.851 --> 30:20.686
       [ Telephone beeps,
          gate buzzes ]

30:34.601 --> 30:35.868
     You Andrew?

30:37.004 --> 30:39.405
    I'm Tiffany.
  Smurf called me.

30:42.743 --> 30:44.743
   May I come in?

30:47.414 --> 30:52.351
                     ♪♪

30:52.419 --> 30:54.686
        She's worried about you.

30:54.755 --> 30:57.556
             Says you need help,
                    uh...

30:57.624 --> 30:58.690
                  relaxing.

30:58.759 --> 31:05.964
                     ♪♪

31:06.033 --> 31:08.567
       [ Fire crackling ]

31:08.635 --> 31:16.708
                     ♪♪

31:16.777 --> 31:25.116
                     ♪♪

31:25.186 --> 31:33.258
                     ♪♪

31:33.326 --> 31:34.526
          Where is he?

31:34.595 --> 31:36.195
        Thought you never wanted
       to see me again, asshole.

31:36.263 --> 31:39.331
      Ox, man.
    Where is he?
           Keep your voice down.

31:43.003 --> 31:44.669
[ Quietly ] His P.O. came by
looking for him, man.

31:44.738 --> 31:46.438
 What's going on?
                     He's dead.

31:51.478 --> 31:52.677
        What?

31:52.746 --> 31:54.880
             Ox, down in Mexico.

31:55.549 --> 31:58.017
       The doctor you sent us to
          tried to patch him up.

31:59.753 --> 32:01.352
                Didn't work.

32:01.354 --> 32:04.956
        Spent two weeks with him
             in some shit motel,

32:05.025 --> 32:06.825
              and then he died.

32:10.764 --> 32:12.564
       Jesus.

32:12.566 --> 32:16.635
                     ♪♪

32:16.703 --> 32:18.037
    Did you tell
    his mom yet?

32:18.105 --> 32:21.140
               You know what?
   W-What was I supposed to say?

32:22.843 --> 32:24.843
                   I mean,
        she thinks he's missing.

32:24.912 --> 32:28.179
                     ♪♪

32:28.249 --> 32:31.250
          Don't try and act like
       you suddenly give a shit.

32:31.318 --> 32:32.584
        [ Tool clatters ]

32:32.653 --> 32:34.119
         You sent us down there.

32:35.923 --> 32:37.856
             It's as much on you
               as it is on me.

32:37.925 --> 32:45.264
                     ♪♪

32:45.332 --> 32:52.071
                     ♪♪

32:52.139 --> 32:55.307
Take off your clothes.
 Leave the heels on.

33:10.891 --> 33:13.125
[ Breathing shakily ]

33:22.436 --> 33:24.169
     Turn over.

33:24.705 --> 33:26.372
                  [ Moans ]

33:33.380 --> 33:34.980
     [ Grunts ]

33:35.048 --> 33:37.448
                 [ Moaning ]

33:37.450 --> 33:42.521
                     ♪♪

33:42.589 --> 33:43.922
      [ Cries ]

33:43.991 --> 33:51.596
                     ♪♪

33:51.665 --> 33:58.670
                     ♪♪

33:58.739 --> 34:01.807
 [ Television plays indistinctly
          in distance ]

34:01.875 --> 34:07.546
                     ♪♪

34:07.614 --> 34:14.018
                     ♪♪

34:14.087 --> 34:16.822
            Heard you were dead.

34:16.889 --> 34:18.956
            You don't look dead.

34:19.025 --> 34:20.826
When did you get out?

34:20.893 --> 34:22.627
 A couple days ago.

34:22.696 --> 34:28.766
                     ♪♪

34:28.835 --> 34:30.268
    I missed you.

34:32.438 --> 34:33.905
    You miss me?

34:33.974 --> 34:39.444
                     ♪♪

34:39.513 --> 34:45.384
                     ♪♪

34:45.452 --> 34:47.518
         [ Horn honks ]

34:47.588 --> 34:50.321
                     ♪♪

34:50.391 --> 34:51.790
  [ Horn honks, tires screech ]

34:51.859 --> 34:56.061
                     ♪♪

34:56.129 --> 34:58.463
          [ No audio ]

34:58.532 --> 35:06.471
                     ♪♪

35:06.540 --> 35:14.413
                     ♪♪

35:14.481 --> 35:22.153
                     ♪♪

35:22.223 --> 35:24.489
      [ Engine sputtering ]

35:24.558 --> 35:31.997
                     ♪♪

35:35.036 --> 35:37.903
      [ Breathing heavily ]

35:37.971 --> 35:46.177
                     ♪♪

35:46.179 --> 35:54.253
                     ♪♪

35:54.321 --> 36:02.527
                     ♪♪

36:02.596 --> 36:04.563
                 [ Sobbing ]

36:06.067 --> 36:07.800
               [ Whimpering ]

36:10.337 --> 36:12.271
 You can't be here,
       Andrew.

36:12.339 --> 36:18.743
                     ♪♪

36:18.812 --> 36:20.211
                 I can't --

36:20.213 --> 36:25.750
                     ♪♪

36:25.819 --> 36:30.956
                     ♪♪

36:31.024 --> 36:32.891
                 [ Sobbing ]
      Okay.

36:32.960 --> 36:37.762
                     ♪♪

36:37.831 --> 36:39.465
                 I lost her.

36:47.774 --> 36:49.641
        [ Knock on door ]

36:49.710 --> 36:51.310
     Woman: Yes?

36:51.378 --> 36:54.279
               Hi. Ms. Oxcama?
         It's, uh -- It's Deran.

36:55.516 --> 36:58.117
              Deran Cody. It --
              I'm Ox's friends.

36:59.987 --> 37:02.321
       Deran?

37:02.389 --> 37:05.124
  Come in. Come in.

37:05.192 --> 37:07.859
                   Gloria:
         I've only got a minute.

37:07.861 --> 37:09.728
             I'm headed to work.

37:09.797 --> 37:12.531
             I haven't seen you
                 in forever.

37:12.599 --> 37:14.333
                How are you?

37:14.401 --> 37:16.335
      I'm good.
    How are you?

37:16.403 --> 37:18.203
                   Better.

37:18.271 --> 37:20.271
             Not quite good yet.

37:20.273 --> 37:21.874
             Seven months sober.

37:23.076 --> 37:24.543
    That's great.

37:26.079 --> 37:28.814
              If you're looking
                for Benito...

37:28.882 --> 37:31.016
             I haven't seen him
               in a long time.

37:31.084 --> 37:39.624
                     ♪♪

37:39.693 --> 37:40.793
        Um...

37:43.164 --> 37:45.497
 [ Sighs ] I, uh...

37:45.566 --> 37:46.832
 [ Exhales deeply ]

37:46.900 --> 37:49.435
               You were always
             such a good friend.

37:52.039 --> 37:53.438
     [ Sniffs ]

37:53.507 --> 37:55.240
                 I gotta go.
     Okay.

37:55.308 --> 38:03.715
                     ♪♪

38:03.717 --> 38:07.820
             If you see Benito,
       tell him that I love him.

38:10.191 --> 38:11.923
                 Okay,<i> mijo.</i>

38:11.925 --> 38:17.996
                     ♪♪

38:18.065 --> 38:20.665
    [ Grunting ]

38:20.734 --> 38:25.937
                     ♪♪

38:25.939 --> 38:27.306
     [ Grunts ]

38:31.412 --> 38:32.611
[ Breathing heavily ]

38:32.679 --> 38:34.546
        You didn't use a condom.

38:34.615 --> 38:36.582
   You'd look good
    with a baby.

38:46.227 --> 38:48.227
   You should have
  come visited me.

38:48.295 --> 38:50.829
       Like you came to visit me
           when I was in County?

38:53.100 --> 38:54.365
 You got any money?

38:54.367 --> 38:55.767
       [ Toilet flushes ]

38:55.769 --> 38:57.469
          You gonna pay me back?

39:06.513 --> 39:08.614
     [ Sniffs ]

39:14.187 --> 39:16.121
    You gotta go.

39:16.189 --> 39:17.188
             Tupi: Why is that?

39:17.258 --> 39:19.658
     'Cause this
   isn't my place.

39:19.727 --> 39:21.760
    He's gonna be
  coming back soon.

39:23.264 --> 39:25.797
                    "He"?

39:25.799 --> 39:27.666
      Yeah, it's this thing
          I'm working.

39:31.404 --> 39:32.871
You gonna cut me in?

39:34.341 --> 39:36.408
               Don't I always?

39:37.878 --> 39:39.378
          Smurf: Deran.

39:42.816 --> 39:44.283
             Craig.

39:47.354 --> 39:48.821
             And J.

39:54.095 --> 39:57.863
      These are the titles
       to our properties.

39:59.032 --> 40:02.968
I tried to split everything up
       fairly between you.

40:04.838 --> 40:08.974
      Being in jail gave me
     a lot of time to think.

40:09.042 --> 40:11.944
   I've held on for too long,
           haven't I?

40:14.982 --> 40:18.650
 You can use those as collateral
   for your house with Adrian.

40:22.589 --> 40:25.390
